<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6598106>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Eutrombicula pacae (Floch and Fauran, 1957), specimen ZIN 9235 (sensilla lost).A—general view, B—dorsal aspect of idiosoma, C—scutum, D—ventral aspect of idiosoma. Scale bars: 100 µm (A), 50 µm (B–D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6598106/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6598108>
    dc:description "FIGURE 17. Eutrombicula pacae (Floch and Fauran, 1957).A—scutum and eyes (specimen ZIN 7219—right), B—dorsal idiosomal seta (specimen ZIN 9226), C—ventral idiosomal seta (specimen ZIN 9226), D—dorsal aspect of idiosoma (specimen ZIN 9249), E—ventral aspect of idiosoma (specimen ZIN 9249), F—dorsal aspect of gnathosoma (specimen ZIN 9226), G—ventral aspect of gnathosoma (specimen ZIN 9226).Abbreviations as in Fig. 2. Scale bars: 50 µm (A), 20 µm (B, C, F, G), 100 µm (D, E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6598108/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6598110>
    dc:description "FIGURE 18. Eutrombicula pacae (Floch and Fauran, 1957), specimen ZIN 9226.A—leg I (trochanter–tarsus), B—leg II (trochanter– tarsus), C—leg III (trochanter–tarsus).Abbreviations as in Fig. 3." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6598110/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

